The paper focuses on motion planning for legged robots, specifically quadrupedal locomotion, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of terrain mapping and analysis, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV) or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
